---
name: Parse and map a BIND named message to OCSF DNS Activity
description: |
  Parses a BIND `named` message body and maps it to OCSF DNS Activity.
---

from {
  time: 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z,
  message: "client @0x7f00 192.0.2.44#53000 (www.example.com): query: www.example.com IN A +E(0)K (192.0.2.53)",
}
named::parse
named::ocsf::map
